{\LARGE Consistent reductions of IIB$^*$/M$^*$ theory and\\[8pt]
de~Sitter supergravity}

\vspace{15pt}

{James T.~Liu$\, ^{*}$, W.~A.~Sabra$\, ^{\dagger}$ and W.~Y.~Wen$\, ^{*,}$%
